author: Vincent Lombardi
message: The spirit, the will to win, and the will to excel, are the things that endure. These qualities are so much more important than the events that occur.
title: Thought of the day

author: Jean-Paul Sartre
message: Man is not sum of what he has already, but rather the sum of what he does not yet have, of what he could have.
title: Thought of the day

author: Richard Bach
message: Don't believe what your eyes are telling you. All they show is limitation. Look with your understanding, find out what you already know, and you'll see the way to fly.
title: Thought of the day

author: Elisabeth Kubler-Ross
message: I believe that we are solely responsible for our choices, and we have to accept the consequences of every deed, word, and thought throughout our lifetime.
title: Thought of the day
